{"id":536556,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/07/【立此存照】模范党员李商隐/","date":"2016-07-30T08:35:32Z","modified":"2016-07-30T08:35:32Z","title":"【立此存照】模范党员李商隐","content":"<blockquote><p><a href=\"http://weibo.com/1918374397/E1czcucdk\" target=\"_blank\">@兰陵笑忘生</a>：原来李商隐才是最早的党员，我党历史要向前推进一千多年了<img title=\"[哈哈]\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/6a/laugh.gif\" alt=\"[哈哈]\" /></p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/725811fdjw1f6bnw4y34cj20qo0zkta6.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-536559\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/725811fdjw1f6bnw4y34cj20qo0zkta6.jpg\" alt=\"725811fdjw1f6bnw4y34cj20qo0zkta6\" width=\"425\" height=\"567\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/725811fdjw1f6bnw4y34cj20qo0zkta6.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/725811fdjw1f6bnw4y34cj20qo0zkta6-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 425px) 100vw, 425px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>以下评论由数字时代编辑收集自新浪微博：</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://weibo.com/3616584504\" target=\"_blank\">@Charlesgooo</a>：商隐君夹在牛李之中不好做人，眼见两党倾轧贪腐，国力式微，作诗以勉之。鼓励各党员发扬包胥九顿哭秦廷的精神，忠义救国，不计得失。没毛病<img title=\"[doge]\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/b6/doge_org.gif\" alt=\"[doge]\" /><img title=\"[doge]\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/b6/doge_org.gif\" alt=\"[doge]\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://weibo.com/2163186783\" target=\"_blank\">@一土人中日生</a>：身无彩凤双飞翼 心有灵犀一点通 这一句诗 说的就是晚唐和当代共产党员对于反腐倡廉的跨越时空的默契<img title=\"[doge]\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/b6/doge_org.gif\" alt=\"[doge]\" /><img title=\"[doge]\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/b6/doge_org.gif\" alt=\"[doge]\" /></p>\n<p>@徐梵筂:【春蚕到死丝方尽，蜡炬成灰泪始干】体现了李商隐作为共产党员鞠躬尽瘁死而后已的伟大理想。</p>\n<p>@听我怒吼HMR：你们竟敢拿唐朝的诗咏本朝的官？！</p>\n<p>@马伯庸：也许是个西班牙人，叫李商隐，前面加“唐”作为敬称，如唐吉诃德。</p>\n<p>@seven耿耿余淮turbo：<strong>作者明明是丁玉标</strong>，哪个上脖颈瘫痪患者安在李商隐头上的？</p>\n<p>@不摸鱼会死星喵：模范党员李商隐，诗词知古又通今，穿越千年来入党，清正廉洁永上心。</p>\n<p>@mindbind：有请著名德国贵族相声演员冯·巩，和著名西班牙贵族相声演员唐·杰忠上台表演</p>\n<p>@智勇小花片：责任编辑荣调党史办</p>\n<p>@宋赵小主：乡亲还打成相亲</p>\n<p>@学术型撩妹汪紫嫣:快来人！我按不住李商隐的棺材了！</p>\n<p>@于赓哲:可以和那个但丁解说汉字列为并蒂莲</p>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/b36f5f00gw1f6bpd6wk76j20zk0qowku.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-536562\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/b36f5f00gw1f6bpd6wk76j20zk0qowku.jpg\" alt=\"b36f5f00gw1f6bpd6wk76j20zk0qowku\" width=\"475\" height=\"356\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/b36f5f00gw1f6bpd6wk76j20zk0qowku.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/b36f5f00gw1f6bpd6wk76j20zk0qowku-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/b36f5f00gw1f6bpd6wk76j20zk0qowku-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 475px) 100vw, 475px\" /></a></p></blockquote>\n<p>@青垚:我不禁献上这张窖藏图</p>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/63243067jw1f6bvcdeth4j20qo0zkaiv.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-536561\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/63243067jw1f6bvcdeth4j20qo0zkaiv.jpg\" alt=\"63243067jw1f6bvcdeth4j20qo0zkaiv\" width=\"375\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/63243067jw1f6bvcdeth4j20qo0zkaiv.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/63243067jw1f6bvcdeth4j20qo0zkaiv-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 375px) 100vw, 375px\" /></a></p></blockquote>\n<p>@懒相饮:不能不上老张了。</p>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/679c263ejw1f6bwczgnbwj20iv0c0t9z.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-536560\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/679c263ejw1f6bwczgnbwj20iv0c0t9z.jpg\" alt=\"679c263ejw1f6bwczgnbwj20iv0c0t9z\" width=\"475\" height=\"302\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/679c263ejw1f6bwczgnbwj20iv0c0t9z.jpg 679w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/07/679c263ejw1f6bwczgnbwj20iv0c0t9z-300x191.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 475px) 100vw, 475px\" /></a></p></blockquote>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,17016,27949],"tags":[20953,31503,11848,28037]}